to\": 1657}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I crashed on Saturday during the course pre-ride and did not think I had a concussion,\\\" Batten explained in an interview with Cyclingnews.\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1811, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1799, \"end\": 1810, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyclingnews.com\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cyclingnews\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyclingnews.com\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyclingnews.com\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1694}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1712}, {\"ngram\": \"a concussion\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1758}, {\"ngram\": \"Batten\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1767}, {\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1793}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the wounds to her face and hand injury, she felt well enough to race the next day.\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1902, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wounds\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1830}, {\"ngram\": \"her face\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1842}, {\"ngram\": \"hand injury\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1858}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She wasn't aware she had suffered a concussion until after she finished in 16th place.\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 1989, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a concussion\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 1949}, {\"ngram\": \"16th place\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 1988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the race, she said, \\\"I passed out and felt really bad after that, and so my symptoms of a concussion, and probably a mix of some heat stuff as well.\\\"\", \"from\": 1991, \"to\": 2146, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2005}, {\"ngram\": \"a concussion\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2097}, {\"ngram\": \"some heat stuff\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2136}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The stress of the race effort brought on severe symptoms that kept her from racing or training for five weeks, meaning she had to miss Worlds and what could have been her best shot at making the team for Paris.\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2358, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2352, \"end\": 2357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7095459258796206e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The stress\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2158}, {\"ngram\": \"the race effort\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2177}, {\"ngram\": \"severe symptoms\", \"from\": 2189, \"to\": 2204}, {\"ngram\": \"racing\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2230}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2242}, {\"ngram\": \"five weeks\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2257}, {\"ngram\": \"Worlds\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2289}, {\"ngram\": \"her best shot\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2328}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 2339, \"to\": 2347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A concussion makes you feel vulnerable, making you aware of how your brain affects your life,\\\" Batten said.\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2468, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A concussion\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2373}, {\"ngram\": \"your brain\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2435}, {\"ngram\": \"your life\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2453}, {\"ngram\": \"Batten\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2462}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It made me reflect a lot on why I do what I do, if I want to continue this - and if I do, what can I do to make sure that I reduce my risks.\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2610, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2494}, {\"ngram\": \"my risks\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was really challenging, with some really hard days,\\\" she admitted.\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2682, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some really hard days\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2666}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it's also beautiful how the body can recover and how you can overcome something like that and return to racing.\", \"from\": 2683, \"to\": 2803, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the body\", \"from\": 2716, \"to\": 2724}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2771}, {\"ngram\": \"racing\", \"from\": 2796, \"to\": 2802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I had some incredible races after that.\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2843, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some incredible races\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2831}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think I have honestly become a smarter and stronger athlete because of that injury.\\\"\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2930, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a smarter and stronger athlete\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 2905}, {\"ngram\": \"that injury\", \"from\": 2917, \"to\": 2928}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mountain biking is a highly technical sport, requiring nerves of steel to tackle steep drops, rock gardens and off-camber loose turns without crashing.\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 3085, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mountain biking\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2949}, {\"ngram\": \"a highly technical sport\", \"from\": 2953, \"to\": 2977}, {\"ngram\": \"nerves\", \"from\": 2989, \"to\": 2995}, {\"ngram\": \"steel\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3004}, {\"ngram\": \"steep drops\", \"from\": 3015, \"to\": 3026}, {\"ngram\": \"rock gardens\", \"from\": 3028, \"to\": 3040}, {\"ngram\": \"off-camber\", \"from\": 3045, \"to\": 3055}, {\"ngram\": \"loose turns\", \"from\": 3056, \"to\": 3067}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A concussion can shatter the confidence that is necessary to be successful in the sport.\", \"from\": 3086, \"to\": 3174, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A concussion\", \"from\": 3086, \"to\": 3098}, {\"ngram\": \"the confidence\", \"from\": 3111, \"to\": 3125}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 3164, \"to\": 3173}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rather than push herself, Batten went back to basics to overcome any trepidation.\", \"from\": 3175, \"to\": 3256, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Batten\", \"from\": 3201, \"to\": 3207}, {\"ngram\": \"basics\", \"from\": 3221, \"to\": 3227}, {\"ngram\": \"any trepidation\", \"from\": 3240, \"to\": 3255}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After my concussion, my body was so stiff and kind of protecting itself that I almost had to relearn how to approach these technical courses and how to choose my lines and how to build that confidence again,\\\" she explained.\", \"from\": 3258, \"to\": 3482, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my concussion\", \"from\": 3265, \"to\": 3278}, {\"ngram\": \"my body\", \"from\": 3280, \"to\": 3287}, {\"ngram\": \"these technical courses\", \"from\": 3376, \"to\": 3399}, {\"ngram\": \"my lines\", \"from\": 3418, \"to\": 3426}, {\"ngram\": \"that confidence\", \"from\": 3444, \"to\": 3459}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It almost took me down to a beginner level again.\", \"from\": 3484, \"to\": 3534, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a beginner level\", \"from\": 3511, \"to\": 3527}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I had to look at these features that used to be a breeze for me and I had to break everything down into pieces and rebuild that belief - take it step by step and allow myself to slow down a little bit and take it one step at a time.\", \"from\": 3535, \"to\": 3767, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these features\", \"from\": 3552, \"to\": 3566}, {\"ngram\": \"a breeze\", \"from\": 3583, \"to\": 3591}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3618, \"to\": 3628}, {\"ngram\": \"pieces\", \"from\": 3639, \"to\": 3645}, {\"ngram\": \"that belief\", \"from\": 3658, \"to\": 3669}, {\"ngram\": \"step\", \"from\": 3688, \"to\": 3692}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 3760, \"to\": 3766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I went to Tucson in the winter for group rides and warmth, and I also continued to return to British Columbia to work on my technical skills,\\\" she elaborated.\", \"from\": 3769, \"to\": 3928, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3780, \"end\": 3786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tucson_station\", \"score\": 0.9242865244841403, \"rank\": 0.08128250942088704, \"text\": \"Tucson\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tucson_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tucson_station\"}, {\"begin\": 3863, \"end\": 3879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Columbia\", \"score\": 0.9999999990022843, \"rank\": 9.973564319600307e-10, \"text\": \"British Columbia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Columbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Columbia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the winter\", \"from\": 3790, \"to\": 3800}, {\"ngram\": \"group rides\", \"from\": 3805, \"to\": 3816}, {\"ngram\": \"warmth\", \"from\": 3821, \"to\": 3827}, {\"ngram\": \"my technical skills\", \"from\": 3891, \"to\": 3910}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After a winter of riding the gnarliest trails she could find, Batten said she was not scared anymore.\", \"from\": 3930, \"to\": 4031, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a winter\", \"from\": 3936, \"to\": 3944}, {\"ngram\": \"the gnarliest trails\", \"from\": 3955, \"to\": 3975}, {\"ngram\": \"Batten\", \"from\": 3992, \"to\": 3998}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think the technical aspect of our sport is what makes it so unique and challenging, and that's what I love about it.\", \"from\": 4033, \"to\": 4152, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the technical aspect\", \"from\": 4042, \"to\": 4062}, {\"ngram\": \"our sport\", \"from\": 4066, \"to\": 4075}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But also it can be scary at times, for sure, and I think that's what makes a race like the Olympics and the course there, where it has a couple of those sections, all that 