n part\", \"from\": 4945, \"to\": 4958}, {\"ngram\": \"our season\", \"from\": 4962, \"to\": 4972}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 4983, \"to\": 4989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Being based here to train, travel less, and focus on race after race, and the recovery in between has really made a difference.\", \"from\": 5007, \"to\": 5135, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"race\", \"from\": 5061, \"to\": 5065}, {\"ngram\": \"race\", \"from\": 5072, \"to\": 5076}, {\"ngram\": \"the recovery\", \"from\": 5082, \"to\": 5094}, {\"ngram\": \"a difference\", \"from\": 5122, \"to\": 5134}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It also allows you to be immersed in the culture and make connections for training.\\\"\", \"from\": 5136, \"to\": 5220, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the culture\", \"from\": 5173, \"to\": 5184}, {\"ngram\": \"connections\", \"from\": 5194, \"to\": 5205}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 5210, \"to\": 5218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Batten planned 2024 around first qualifying for the Olympics and then building up toward Paris.\", \"from\": 5222, \"to\": 5317, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5311, \"end\": 5316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7095459258796206e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Batten\", \"from\": 5222, \"to\": 5228}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5270, \"to\": 5282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I broke it into two parts.\", \"from\": 5319, \"to\": 5346, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two parts\", \"from\": 5336, \"to\": 5345}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So part one was the qualification period, which was the two World Cups in Brazil,\\\" where she was third in Mairipo\\u00e3 and won in Arax\\u00e1, \\\"and also the third World Cup in Nov\\u00e9 Mesto, the Czech Republic [where she finished second to Pauline Ferrand-Pr\\u00e9vot].\", \"from\": 5347, \"to\": 5598, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5421, \"end\": 5427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9997044392085023, \"rank\": 0.00029564449823080786, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 5473, \"end\": 5478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arax\\u00e1\", \"score\": 0.9239214528466035, \"rank\": 0.06999999999997611, \"text\": \"Arax\\u00e1\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arax\\u00e1\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arax\\u00e1\"}, {\"begin\": 5574, \"end\": 5596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pauline_Ferrand-Pr\\u00e9vot\", \"score\": 0.9999998852627024, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pauline Ferrand-Pr\\u00e9vot\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pauline_Ferrand-Pr\\u00e9vot\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pauline_Ferrand-Pr\\u00e9vot\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 5350, \"to\": 5354}, {\"ngram\": \"the qualification period\", \"from\": 5363, \"to\": 5387}, {\"ngram\": \"the two World Cups\", \"from\": 5399, \"to\": 5417}, {\"ngram\": \"Mairipo\\u00e3\", \"from\": 5453, \"to\": 5461}, {\"ngram\": \"also the third World Cup\", \"from\": 5485, \"to\": 5509}, {\"ngram\": \"Nov\\u00e9 Mesto\", \"from\": 5513, \"to\": 5523}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those three races were included in our qualification period.\", \"from\": 5599, \"to\": 5659, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Those three races\", \"from\": 5599, \"to\": 5616}, {\"ngram\": \"our qualification period\", \"from\": 5634, \"to\": 5658}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wanted to nail that so that I could just focus on Olympic day.\\\"\", \"from\": 5660, \"to\": 5725, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic day\", \"from\": 5712, \"to\": 5723}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having made the team, Batten turned her focus to working on tactics, equipment and skills over results.\", \"from\": 5727, \"to\": 5830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 5739, \"to\": 5747}, {\"ngram\": \"Batten\", \"from\": 5749, \"to\": 5755}, {\"ngram\": \"her focus\", \"from\": 5763, \"to\": 5772}, {\"ngram\": \"tactics\", \"from\": 5787, \"to\": 5794}, {\"ngram\": \"equipment\", \"from\": 5796, \"to\": 5805}, {\"ngram\": \"skills\", \"from\": 5810, \"to\": 5816}, {\"ngram\": \"results\", \"from\": 5822, \"to\": 5829}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She finished eighth in Val di Sole, then dropped out of the Crans-Montana World Series race at the end of June after suffering a minor injury during the short track race.\", \"from\": 5831, \"to\": 6001, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5891, \"end\": 5904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crans-Montana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Crans-Montana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crans-Montana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crans-Montana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Val di Sole\", \"from\": 5854, \"to\": 5865}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 5926, \"to\": 5933}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 5937, \"to\": 5941}, {\"ngram\": \"a minor injury\", \"from\": 5958, \"to\": 5972}, {\"ngram\": \"the short track race\", \"from\": 5980, \"to\": 6000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She chose to skip the Les Gets World Series race in early July to focus on preparing for the Olympics and dropped to third in the overall standings.\", \"from\": 6002, \"to\": 6150, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Les\", \"from\": 6020, \"to\": 6027}, {\"ngram\": \"World Series race\", \"from\": 6033, \"to\": 6050}, {\"ngram\": \"early July\", \"from\": 6054, \"to\": 6064}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 6091, \"to\": 6103}, {\"ngram\": \"the overall standings\", \"from\": 6128, \"to\": 6149}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everything I do in these races is really just focused on race execution and my equipment so that everything is dialled once I get to Paris - my tyres, my bike, my suspension, my nutrition, how I am going to hydrate, how I am going to cool down, how I am going to warm up,\\\" Batten said she wants to make sure \\\"all these little details are just absolutely nailed.\\\"\", \"from\": 6154, \"to\": 6517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6288, \"end\": 6293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7095459258796206e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everything\", \"from\": 6155, \"to\": 6165}, {\"ngram\": \"these races\", \"from\": 6174, \"to\": 6185}, {\"ngram\": \"race execution\", \"from\": 6212, \"to\": 6226}, {\"ngram\": \"my equipment\", \"from\": 6231, \"to\": 6243}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 6252, \"to\": 6262}, {\"ngram\": \"my bike\", \"from\": 6306, \"to\": 6313}, {\"ngram\": \"my suspension\", \"from\": 6315, \"to\": 6328}, {\"ngram\": \"my nutrition\", \"from\": 6330, \"to\": 6342}, {\"ngram\": \"Batten\", \"from\": 6428, \"to\": 6434}, {\"ngram\": \"all these little details\", \"from\": 6464, \"to\": 6488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having already made her debut at the Olympics in Tokyo in 2021, Batten does not have to worry about the unknowns of living in the Olympic Village and everything that being at the world's largest sporting event entails.\", \"from\": 6519, \"to\": 6737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6568, \"end\": 6573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9750763656456365, \"rank\": 0.02551559852659889, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/res